column4: NSLOCTEXT("[1CF28BD140183234CB501D9EC581739B]", "E0E3AB66411478DE52A44FB49A958B53", "Time is slow here. Half a day here is like a day out there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1CF28BD140183234CB501D9EC581739B]", "6F5A6944448BBF777379B581F5936276", "For those who want to rest, it\'s perfect.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1CF28BD140183234CB501D9EC581739B]", "81C5C7794F0DB341B8AEA693A3C37CBD", "Time goes fast in the Speedy Time Zone. It\'s just beyond here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1CF28BD140183234CB501D9EC581739B]", "8B6157CC4C3D5476F894FD89247C4AA1", "Two days pass instead of one there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1CF28BD140183234CB501D9EC581739B]", "0E4DC1A749FC5C74496EF8800EE8EC23", "Your Digimon grows faster, but fades away faster too.")
